### Obtener todos los inquilinos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener inquilino por id
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos?id=2
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener inquilinos por nombre
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos?nombre_completo=aLex
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener inquilinos por tipo de identificacion
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos?tipo_identificacion=Cedula
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener inquilinos activos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos?status=true
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener inquilinos inactivos
GET http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos?status=true
Content-Type: application/json

### Crear inquilino - correcto
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan Perez Lopez saeloo",
  "status": true,
  "telefono": "09912345678",
  "email": "juan@gmail.com",
  "numero_identificacion": "12345678901",
  "tipo_identificacion": "Cedula"
}

### Crear inquilino - numero de identificacion existente
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan Perez Lopez saeloo",
  "status": true,
  "telefono": "09912345678",
  "email": "juan@gmail.com",
  "numero_identificacion": "1234567890",
  "tipo_identificacion": "Cedula"
}

### Crear inquilino - email invalido
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan Perez Lopez",
  "telefono": "0991234567",
  "email": "correo-invalido",
  "numero_identificacion": "1234567890",
  "tipo_identificacion": "Cedula"
}

### Crear inquilino - tipo identificacion invalido
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan Perez Lopez",
  "telefono": "0991234567",
  "email": "juan@gmail.com",
  "numero_identificacion": "1234567890",
  "tipo_identificacion": "DNI"
}

### Crear inquilino - nombre muy corto
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan",
  "telefono": "0991234567",
  "email": "juan@gmail.com",
  "numero_identificacion": "1234567890",
  "tipo_identificacion": "Cedula"
}

### Crear inquilino - sin campos requeridos
POST http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre_completo": "Juan Perez Lopez 2"
}

### Actualizar inquilino - correcto
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefono": "0997654321",
  "status": false
}

### Actualizar inquilino - id inexistente
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefono": "0997654321"
}

### Actualizar inquilino - tipo identificacion invalido
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipo_identificacion": "DNI"
}

### Eliminar inquilino - correcto
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Eliminar inquilino - id inexistente
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/inquilinos/9999
Content-Type: application/json